{"tid":824183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國人突然暴富的錢是從哪裡來的？ 　 兩個字：印的！ 　 2018年中國發行的人民幣(即廣義貨幣M2)，是174萬億元","createTime":"2018-09-17T03:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T05:05:45.000Z","uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b44544eb4e3d717cd758ceca6650c19b2a6364","tid":824183,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"「中國人突然暴富的錢是從哪裡來的？<br />\n　<br />\n兩個字：印的！<br />\n　<br />\n2018年中國發行的人民幣(即廣義貨幣M2)，是174萬億元，相當於27.19萬億美元，這個數字，超過2018年美國發行的美元(14萬億)和歐洲發行的歐元(13.12萬億)的總和。<br />\n　<br />\n中國投放的人民幣(M2)從2008年的40萬億，飛躍到2018年的174萬億的。它直觀地顯示了：中國人是怎樣暴富的。」"},{"pid":"91687a81c32ca0ccda97fd035fd3ad0cc8443bfd","tid":824183,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:44:29.000Z","msg":"匯率控制國"},{"pid":"d4f91e023dfbf172a7f286a0569f293dea4c1ee2","tid":824183,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"其實係獨裁國家印銀行係唔係任你印幾多都得?  有人話印得多就會通漲升得多, 好似委內瑞拉咁 , 但大陸通漲又唔見升太多, 所以無影響?"},{"pid":"96c6899d868dd38e4fa49d22af82cc3100941f98","tid":824183,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"115943b269cfc7cab3a20afd0a4f435fd879e83e","tid":824183,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59078185576d34281d20f5332685632c93502864","tid":824183,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"2008之後美國QE緊，所以印人仔對匯率影響唔大，<br />\n但而家美國收緊返銀根，其他跟住美國印銀紙既國家就會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋大陸通漲得好勁，諗下當年搵萬三都可以包二奶既時代，而家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac